====Template:lop usage====
Enter <nowiki>{{</nowiki>'''lop'''|''patch name''|''OTTD version''|''forum thread id''|''notes''<nowiki>}}</nowiki> in between {{en/S|en/Archive/Community/Lop header}} and {{en/S|en/Archive/Community/Lop footer}} templates.<br />
Enter <nowiki>{{</nowiki>'''lop'''|''patch pack name''|''OTTD version''|''forum thread id''|''list of patches and notes''<nowiki>}}</nowiki> in between {{en/S|en/Archive/Community/Lop pack header}} and {{en/S|en/Archive/Community/Lop footer}} templates. 

Example:
<pre>
===Eyecandy===
{{en/Archive/Community/Lop header}}
{{en/Archive/Community/Lop|More GUI icons|r123456, 1.2.3|123456|4={{en/Flyspray|123456}}, also see [http://www.link.com/index?id=123456 this page]}}
{{en/Archive/Community/Lop footer}}
</pre>
<pre>
==Patch packs==
{{en/Archive/Community/Lop pack header}}
{{en/Archive/Community/Lop|GUI patch pack|r123456, 1.2.3|123456|
More GUI icons<br />
Extended station list
}}
{{en/Archive/Community/Lop footer}}
</pre>
Notes:
#Use "4=" for the notes parameter if the note contains an equal sign (=).
